title: BioImage Model Zoo: Advanced models in one-click
questions: Who participates in the BioImage Model Zoo?

objectives: Share what BioImage Model Zoo is.

key_points: The BioImage Model Zoo is a community-driven AI model repository to facilitate the adoption of AI methods among the bioimage community by providing easy access to pretrained AI models.
